==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Limax
<hw>Li"max</hw> <pr>(l⟦imac⟧"m⟦acr⟧ks)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[L.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A genus of airbreathing
mollusks, including the common garden slugs. They have a small
rudimentary shell. The breathing pore is on the right side of the neck.
Several species are troublesome in gardens. See <er>Slug</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Limb</ent>⟦br⟧
